{"tid":1720562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曱甴：（撐警遊行）好多市民好忙 喺一至兩個鐘前前先知會警方","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:25:13.000Z","uid":216992,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0df5645e8f627d80f28103015bd979a355d3f0ba","tid":1720562,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"今日下午元朗有逾百人參與撐警遊行，要求政府盡快止亂制暴，保護市民。在警方記者會上，有傳媒關注有關遊行事前有否通知警方，並申請不反對通知書。警方行動部高級警司汪威遜回應時指，根據手上資料，相關團體未有提早知會警方。他提醒市民集會及遊行前要通知警方，又說「好多市民好忙」，在一至兩小時前才知會警方，他強調警方會盡量配合市民表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%EF%BC%9F%E8%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%83-196503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25EF%25BC%259F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%2597%25A9%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259C%2583-196503&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVcyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=739145c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83%E3%80%91%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%EF%BC%9F%E8%AD%A6%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E7%9F%A5%E6%9C%83-196503</a>"},{"pid":"a0642831a965aabb141e8fe4f019195f39f4cfad","tid":1720562,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re